<li id="footnote-6YU8"><p>In truth I‚Äôve spent the past couple of years studiously avoiding what felt like the fancy bits of both Obsidian and my Apple devices; no wonder it‚Äôs taken me so long!<a href="#ref-6YU8" class="footnote-back" role="doc-backlink"><span class="small-caps">‚Ü©Ô∏é</span></a></p></li>
